Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteMaterial

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteMaterial
public class JDBWasteMaterial extends Object
The JDBWasteMaterial class updates the table APP_WASTE_MATERIAL. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Location as stored in the APP_WASTE_MATERIAL table.
